# Main Features Roadmap

# Phase 1 — Foundation Setup

Goal:
Create a functional local AI chat system.

Features:
* Chat UI
* Ollama integration
* Streaming responses
* Basic backend API
* Conversation history
* Markdown rendering


# Phase 2 — Memory System
Features:
* Semantic memory
* Embedding generation
* Conversation summarization
* Persistent chat sessions


# Phase 3 — RAG System
Features:
* PDF uploads
* Document chunking
* Embeddings
* Semantic retrieval
* Context injection

# Phase 4 — AI Tools
Features:
* File search
* Folder summarization
* Tool calling
* Local automation

# Phase 5 — Advanced Features
Features:
* Voice input
* Desktop app
* AI agents
* Multi-workspace support
* Plugin system